### Test User Registration
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Test User Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Test Session Validation (requires token from login)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/validate-session
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Test Get Active Sessions (requires token from login)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/active-sessions
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Test Logout Other Devices (requires token from login)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout-other-devices
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Test User Profile (requires token from login)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/user/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Test Logout (requires token from login)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Variables
@baseUrl = https://localhost:7001
@authToken = your-jwt-token-here
